! Comments begin with a "!" character.
! this file configures the appearance of uxterm and xterm terminals
! To apply it for this session you need to run
!   xrdb -merge ~/.Xresources
!
! To make it effective across sessions you need to add it to the autostart
! file of the window manager. Eg: xfce4-session-settings

